description: This skill will teach you a little about our fair city located in Southwest Virginia. The city is one of many cultural events and beautiful locations. The skill uses standard invocations and is available for all versions of the Alexa platform. No special accounts or hardware is required. This skill will give out a few facts. Ask your Alexa enabled device "Open Roanoke Guide" and you will learn small details about the area.
exampleInteractions: "Alexa, Ask Roanoke Guide to tell me about Roanoke."
name: Roanoke, Virginia Guide
shortDescription: A skill to learn more about the Star City of Virginia, Roanoke.
